modules.description: This module establishes WebSocket connections to Gremlin servers and sends Gremlin queries, handling responses as JSON or error statuses. It provides functions to run single queries or batches within a transaction, returning parsed results or detailed failure reasons. The module works directly with WebSocket frames, JSON values, and Gremlin-specific message statuses for query execution and session management.

This module connects to Gremlin servers via WebSocket, sends queries, and processes responses as JSON or error statuses. It supports running individual queries or batches in a transaction, returning parsed results or detailed errors. Key data types include WebSocket frames, JSON values, and Gremlin message statuses. You can execute Gremlin scripts, manage sessions, and handle query results or failures directly.
